data.description: Welcome to 6840 Overview Ct. in Park Lake! This impeccably crafted home offers an ideal haven for you and your family. This home is in a prime location with ease of access to shopping, AUM, Baptist East on a peaceful cul-de-sac. As you step into the foyer, natural light floods the interior, creating a welcoming atmosphere. The open-concept layout enhances the flow from room to room, fostering a sense of space and connectivity. The well-appointed kitchen boasts granite countertops and ample cabinet space. Retreat to the master bedroom for a peaceful escape, providing a cozy and comfortable setting for a restful night's sleep. The very spacious master bathroom boasts one walk-in closet, ensuring an organized and clutter-free environment. The master bath also features separate vanities, a jetted tub, and a walk-in tiled shower.  The upstairs has 1 bonus room with plenty of space. The bonus room offers ample square footage for design possibilities where you can let your imagination run wild and create the space of your dreams. Extend your living space outdoors to dine, entertain, and revel in the beauty of your surroundings. The outdoor has a full privacy fence ideal for gatherings, celebrations, or quiet moments of reflection. The yard, perfectly sized for hosting gatherings or enjoying the fresh air, completes the picture of an ideal home. The home is also pre-wired for a security system. Don't miss the opportunity to call this one home! Contact me today to schedule a viewing and embark on the journey to your new home.
